      • signIn

        public void signIn(java.lang.String email,
                   java.lang.String password)
        Description copied from interface: com.cse110team24.walkwalkrevolution.firebase.auth.Auth
        Signs in a user to this service's provider, given email and password.

        On success, a call to AuthSubject.notifyObserversSignedIn(IUser) is made with the sign in user.

        On failure, a call to AuthSubject.notifyObserversSignInError(Auth.AuthError) is made with the AuthError that occurred.

        Specified by:
        signIn in interface com.cse110team24.walkwalkrevolution.firebase.auth.Auth
        Parameters:
        email - the existing user's email
        password - the existing user's password

        Description copied from interface: com.cse110team24.walkwalkrevolution.firebase.auth.Auth
        Signs up a user to this service's provider given email, password, and display name and automatically signs the user into the provider.
